ous. I was so thankful that I could watch the battle but can't do anything. The pally saw my blue HP bar, and started casting some heal. I stood right back up and went right back into battle with a silver of health while the pally now stood back and kept healing me. Much to my dismay, Maestro saw me and blew another deadly double attack strike. This time the pally healing can't save me. I was knocked unconcous for the second time (yeah really). But somehow, Maetro got distracted and left my bloody body alone. But God shine on me again. I got a Lay on Hand from our good pally. I stood right back up, full health and quick taunt the bad Maestro back on me. I called out a battle cry and defty put a few good backstabs. He spunned right back to me, and tried to kill me with his squad attack. But it was two late. He was running out of health, and he started running for his life. I chased him down and backstabbed him to dead, sweet revenge at last. Maestro was slained and this vile rogue stands tall for another day. And I didn't forget to thank the enchanter, the clerics and the pally who saved my life, not one but TWICE.<br>
<br>
PS: after the battle, i found out that another cleric also full health me when I was unconcous. 8*) unconcous twice and still able to finish Maestro!! whooppee<br>
<br>
PPS: Maestro dropped the suckest sword: erudite only pally sword. Who ever see an erudian pally? whoot.<br>
<br>
Pubin Dethief<br>
Lv47 Half elf on Solusek Ro<br>
